Issues.Body:
I'm facing a weird issue due to httpclient, when i set some HttpHeaders(not content-type), content-type changes to text/plain in production build, while in local content-type is application/json. 
Due to this my server responds with Http error 415(unsupported media type) as it can only handle application/json requests, and furthermore, this issue isn't reproducible all the time.
My understanding is that content-type by default should always be application/json.




### Affected Package
"@angular/http": "^6.0.3",
"angular": "^1.6.9",
"@angular/common": "^6.0.3",




